ss.  The only nucyalur references made were to North Korea and Iraq.  However, the harder part might be convincing Kaku and Zubrin.  Kaku doesn't seem particularly confrontational, and Zubrin might be unwilling considering the flack he took after the debate with the Lunar and Planetary Institute's Paul Spudis.  <br>
